Stasis
Discworld ritual help
Stasis

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Stasis - Traps your target into a crystal sphere.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This is an offensive ritual which, when performed, removes the target
from your presence by trapping them into a sphere of crystal.  You
will need a prayer book and some incense to perform this ritual.
.EP
